ich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.936175','2025-10-29 02:04:28.936175',NULL),(1444,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\">To facilitate such arrangement where industry reaches NE; have physical presence there; adopt and do capacity building of SHGs for skill; branding, marketing etc.</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,2,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.943147','2025-10-29 02:04:28.943147',NULL),(1445,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Buyer to decide location of Central Processing Units/ clusters.</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,3,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.950702','2025-10-29 02:04:28.950702',NULL),(1446,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\"><b>Proposal for Bamboo to be used for Partition and Wall Panels as part of PM AwasYojana in NE. This could also be an agenda point for NEC Plenary</b></font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,4,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.958971','2025-10-29 02:04:28.958971',NULL),(1447,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\">Quality Control and Product Certification to be done in collaboration with Industry</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,5,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.965931','2025-10-29 02:04:28.965931',NULL),(1448,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Revised presentations held on 23/09, 16/10, 18/12.<b> Following Action Points:&nbsp;</b></font>',NULL,1,'decimal',0,6,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.971748','2025-10-29 02:04:28.971748',NULL),(1449,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Comprehensive value chain analysis with role of each stakeholder (GoI, NECBDC, Market Players etc.) clearly and completely defined</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,7,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.979560','2025-10-29 02:04:28.979560',NULL),(1450,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">How each Stakeholder is adding value to the chain to be clearly laid out</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,8,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.985883','2025-10-29 02:04:28.985883',NULL),(1451,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\" color=\"#00ff00\">Stakeholders to visit interested States/ Sites and work on the complete value addition plan with NECBDC - (Done)</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',1,9,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:28.993258','2025-10-29 02:04:28.993258',NULL),(1452,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\" color=\"#00ff00\">Buyers to physically visit and interact - All Time Plastic Co. and Amazon - visited the cluster developed by NECBDC and interacted with the artisans.</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',1,10,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.002807','2025-10-29 02:04:29.002807',NULL),(1453,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\"><b>Action items w.r.t. NECBDC presentation held on 15.01.2025</b></font>',NULL,1,'decimal',0,11,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.020701','2025-10-29 02:04:29.020701',NULL),(1454,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">ATP Model</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,12,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.036156','2025-10-29 02:04:29.036156',NULL),(1455,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Common plan (Gantt chart) from ideation to execution between ATP &amp; MDoNER.&nbsp;</font>',NULL,3,'lower-roman',0,13,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.061233','2025-10-29 02:04:29.061233',NULL),(1456,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Expectations/ Demand of ATP from DoNER and Expectations/ Demand of DoNER from ATP</font>',NULL,3,'lower-roman',0,14,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.070148','2025-10-29 02:04:29.070148',NULL),(1457,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\">Bottom to up approach to be followed; Focus on Cluster/ SHGs based approach</font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,15,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.077339','2025-10-29 02:04:29.077339',NULL),(1458,24,NULL,'<div><font size=\"2\">Marketplace Model</font></div><div><br></div>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,16,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.087632','2025-10-29 02:04:29.087632',NULL),(1459,24,NULL,'<div><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Common plan (Gantt chart) from ideation to execution between Amazon &amp; MDoNER.&nbsp;</span></div>',NULL,3,'lower-roman',0,17,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.095891','2025-10-29 02:04:29.095891',NULL),(1460,24,NULL,'<div><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Common plan (Gantt chart) from ideation to execution between Amazon &amp; MDoNER.&nbsp;</span></div>',NULL,3,'lower-roman',0,18,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.102578','2025-10-29 02:04:29.102578',NULL),(1461,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Rough estimate for prospective sales (monthly) for FY 25-26 to be projected as targets. Each Cluster to have its own GST</font>',NULL,1,'decimal',0,19,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.110776','2025-10-29 02:04:29.110776',NULL),(1462,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\"><b><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">Amazon and ATP revised presentations</span> were held on 18.02.2025. Below are the Action Points:</b></font>',NULL,1,'decimal',0,20,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.115634','2025-10-29 02:04:29.115634',NULL),(1463,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\"><b>Amazon:</b></font>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,21,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.123349','2025-10-29 02:04:29.123349',NULL),(1464,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Revised PPT was held on <b>11.03.2025</b>. Below are the action points:</font>',NULL,3,'lower-roman',0,22,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.129725','2025-10-29 02:04:29.129725',NULL),(1465,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\"><b>Since Amazon model doesn\'t require CAPEX contribution from Ministry, it can be taken forward duly adhering to the existing rules</b></font>',NULL,4,'bullet',0,23,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.136686','2025-10-29 02:04:29.136686',NULL),(1466,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Identification of products and SHGs Amazon/any other such platform wants to work with.</font>',NULL,4,'bullet',0,24,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.142570','2025-10-29 02:04:29.142570',NULL),(1467,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\">DoNER to only focus on developing production stage of the value chain like CFCs, Finishing Units, Skilling Up of Artisans etc; which is actually going to help the identified SHGs/ Clusters</font>',NULL,4,'bullet',0,25,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.148708','2025-10-29 02:04:29.148708',NULL),(1468,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\"><b>NECBDC prepared DPR - Concept note cleared by SEC; RFP uploaded on 30.06.2025, DPR has been uploaded on portal on 08.07.2025 under SoNEC. Bid submission deadline was 15.08.2025,&nbsp; EIMC meeting chaired by secy. NEC to be held on 28.08.2025. Secy to decide on participation by -20/08</b></font>','2025-08-20 00:00:00.000000',2,'lower-alpha',0,26,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.156070','2025-10-29 02:04:29.156070',NULL),(1469,24,NULL,'<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\"><font size=\"2\"><b>ATP</b></font></span>',NULL,2,'lower-alpha',0,27,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.165479','2025-10-29 02:04:29.165479',NULL),(1470,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Responsibility matrix involving all the stakeholders from NECBDS, Assam Government, DoNER and ATP across each part of the value chain to be defined.</font>',NULL,3,'lower-roman',0,28,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.172666','2025-10-29 02:04:29.172666',NULL),(1471,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Secretary, MDoNER to set up a small group comprising of 4 representatives – MDoNER, Govt. of Assam, NECBDC, ATP for steering the initiative before next presentation.</font>',NULL,3,'lower-roman',0,29,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.179498','2025-10-29 02:04:29.179498',NULL),(1472,24,NULL,'<div><font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\">Above 4 Steering group members to be physically present during next presentation next week</font></div><div><font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\"><b><br></b></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\"><b>Revised presentation was held on 05.03.2025. Below are the action points:</b></font></div>',NULL,3,'lower-roman',0,30,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.188224','2025-10-29 02:04:29.188224',NULL),(1473,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">Detailed role and CAPEX contribution of each player in the value chain</font>',NULL,4,'bullet',0,31,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.197337','2025-10-29 02:04:29.197337',NULL),(1474,24,NULL,'<font face=\"Arial Narrow, serif\" size=\"2\">NECBDC to redo the presentation and share</font>',NULL,4,'bullet',0,32,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.205532','2025-10-29 02:04:29.205532',NULL),(1475,24,NULL,'<font size=\"2\"><b>Bids have been opened on 25.07.2025. Technical evaluation is under process and will be finalized by 18.08.2025.DPR has been sent to IIM, Shillong for their comments and will be uploaded on the portal by 20.08.2025</b></font>','2025-08-19 00:00:00.000000',3,'lower-roman',0,33,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 02:04:29.214744','2025-10-29 02:04:29.214744',NULL),(1476,29,NULL,'<font size=\"2\">vnm</font>',NULL,1,'decimal',0,1,'rich_text',NULL,'2025-10-29 15:33:28.669197','2025-10-29 15:33:28.669197',NULL);
